{"tid":28170,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱上本民前fb睇返舊片 真係好唏噓","createTime":"2016-12-07T18:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T01:49:47.000Z","uid":44438,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1c8ff912db726a5ff61303bf01f9c1bb638b7ac0","tid":28170,"uid":44438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:59:44.000Z","msg":"本土派啲氣焰去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起雨革<br />\n諗返以前光復個勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但之後天琦俾人dq<br />\n依家到梁游 仲有四個都就快dq埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加加埋埋呢堆議員嘅選民其實唔少<br />\n俾人恰到上心口 <br />\n都仲係全部啞哂<br />\n香港人真係冇底線可以繼續忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明白大家都有工作要生活 <br />\n但都唔一定要講不了 <br />\n多啲人關心都可以攞返個勢 疊馬啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔一定集到氣 唔一定有用<br />\n不如都認認真真諗下有咩可以做 <br />\n<br />\n對唔住其實我知我講到好空泛 一舊舊咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想多啲人一齊反思下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b36bfa7743f0373e7c365e3b5df11d4af274d30","tid":28170,"uid":9028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T19:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89509dd0d89be3fd5bccee5427f9eb22af284cb8","tid":28170,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T19:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b948a2b23b79905766b24309b4bef7c853094173","tid":28170,"uid":51371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T19:40:20.000Z","msg":"自從立會選舉左膠大勝本土 我已經決定唔再理<br />\n冇得救 我會做港豬 香港人係抵死"},{"pid":"98cb10d85da10ecfc465423a298e7ce7099e2ed4","tid":28170,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:46:53.000Z","msg":"本土派氣焰畀人食熱狗食晒啦<br />\n仲好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245e9821bddab709388a0f761c392627b563f90a","tid":28170,"uid":44438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:09:32.000Z","msg":"講到我都<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b13f1f8b0b71cf78158b4f79ab0acc566d12df3","tid":28170,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c6f1a7845aa2b824f77e612279386d18e878b3","tid":28170,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:01:50.000Z","msg":"敗於私怨同弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9c47bb24958298257930710eef5aa08e0d593d","tid":28170,"uid":635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自從立會選舉左膠大勝本土 我已經決定唔再理<br />\n冇得救 我會做港豬 香港人係抵死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n倒番轉諗，民主本身就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90807cdec4b716d91eed692f77648531da0bc2b9","tid":28170,"uid":36188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440f6913735be141573a70f115992a8acd578b1c","tid":28170,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本土派氣焰畀人食熱狗食晒啦<br />\n仲好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真，比班一受人質疑就一句「你食熱狗」「你係本青狗」既熱狗消磨哂"},{"pid":"5dc7bd2dd0cbfc176baa54a0ccbe6e1761799007","tid":28170,"uid":11979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本土派氣焰畀人食熱狗食晒啦<br />\n仲好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真，比班一受人質疑就一句「你食熱狗」「你係本青狗」既熱狗消磨哂</blockquote><br />\n呢個勢真係幾有有希望既意識形態都好<br />\n都會輸個勢 好似班中坑藍絲咁...唉"},{"pid":"bccf02c8d52de1d721ce0800a75d6e516540d8d6","tid":28170,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:22:33.000Z","msg":"雨革都係屎忽撞棍咋<br />\n你估佢想咩"},{"pid":"5fb83ca0c0080d85d260f79739530ea990d4145c","tid":28170,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T09:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本土派氣焰畀人食熱狗食晒啦<br />\n仲好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真，比班一受人質疑就一句「你食熱狗」「你係本青狗」既熱狗消磨哂</blockquote><br />\n哦！你又食熱狗！"},{"pid":"7f49794b489e25d44a9f55151a2f1fac29aec170","tid":28170,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"不如諗下背水一戰既情況<br />\n<br />\n何謂背水一戰？<br />\n後無退路之時唯有勇者無懼而殺出血路<br />\n<br />\n宜家香港要和理非非先係主流，和理非非唔係無用，但係成效太低<br />\n<br />\n所謂本土派(本民青、熱狗)又係到互咬<br />\n呢段爭執都唔知幾時停<br />\n<br />\n不如自己準備，自己做事<br />\n<br />\n遲下再補充"},{"pid":"b30d40c5ce9a27987846439fd1ba797d6346da84","tid":28170,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:46:02.000Z","msg":"本熱互屌 本土派亡"},{"pid":"981fc65389e4906cdf6892b19bcea1cf1b9e250b","tid":28170,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bbaf8705db7d97cd93eabe775e72c16ab91da79","tid":28170,"uid":35236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"本土派內鬨真係好on9 <br />\n冇啦 玩完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8e6b8f22d95481c07e240a77024dab670b37d9","tid":28170,"uid":35236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"本土派內鬨真係好on9 <br />\n冇啦 玩完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7a982d514b16c7517a4822541f923247677cce","tid":28170,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:18:57.000Z","msg":"主要係因為港共全力打壓，抗爭成本太大"},{"pid":"90cc08172